{"tid":402721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙軍警檢走加泰公投物資 全力阻止獨立公投","createTime":"2017-09-16T15:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T17:19:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f98116a1626d255668dae72fe4f7d28f5fcc4ce2","tid":402721,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T15:47:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/59bd3aabe603838a1b6c90ca\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F59bd3aabe603838a1b6c90ca&d=d04HESv6TTg9hnhmXNSde8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=0b609aac\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/59bd3aabe603838a1b6c90ca</a><br />\n<br />\n西班牙加泰羅尼亞地區下月1日將舉行獨立公投，中央政府全力阻止。軍警搜查多個地點，檢走公投物資。<br />\n<br />\n在加泰羅尼亞首府巴塞羅那，軍警突擊搜查一間印刷公司，檢走獨立公投的選票、票箱及傳單等。有民眾到場抗議，批評馬德里當局阻撓公投。<br />\n<br />\n軍警也搜查報社等地點，連串行動，又檢獲10萬張海報。<br />\n<br />\n加泰羅尼亞自治區主席普伊格德蒙特，聯同區內700多位表明支持公投的市長，在巴塞羅那集會造勢。<br />\n<br />\n馬德里政府一直指公投非法，早前傳召自治區內市長查問他們取態，又威脅如果不接受傳召，可能會被拘捕。"},{"pid":"24ea832027acb155ccc4c05092812765c571a98e","tid":402721,"uid":94824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:23:15.000Z","msg":"天下烏鴉一撚樣黑"},{"pid":"93ab60cee5f00d386892573878d8bd693770c88e","tid":402721,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天下烏鴉一撚樣黑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但冇咁黑，淨係拎走你d野, 冇打死你d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98fbf805fe136618f1d6e6af33b8a221d733bb7","tid":402721,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天下烏鴉一撚樣黑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但冇咁黑，淨係拎走你d野, 冇打死你d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幫獨派拉票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你睇下英國對蘇格蘭公投既做法, 聰明好多！"},{"pid":"becdf5cf65308b3fd56c51f898c6027bd45f40bf","tid":402721,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,